  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Melia Madeira Mare is available on bed &amp; breakfast and half-board. </p>
<p>Breakfast is a delicious buffet breakfast with hot and cold options. Those on half-board basis can enjoy dinner in the Mare Nostrum Buffet Restaurant.</p>
<p>The hotels restaurants and bars (bookable and payable locally):</p>
<p><strong>Mare Nostrum Buffet Restaurant</strong> offers contemporary design an indoor dining area and outdoor terrace. The buffet offers tasty international cuisine.</p>
<p><strong>Il Massimo Restaurant</strong> serves an innovative menu with the an indoor restaurant and outdoor terrace.</p>
<p><strong>Bar O Ilhéu</strong> is located by the pool and is great for a drink as well as light lunches and snacks.</p>
<p><strong>La Luna Bar</strong> has fantastic views towards the ocean and has live music on some evenings.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
