<p><strong><span>Additional hotel facilities: </span></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>260m² outdoor pool</li>
<li>Indoor pool</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Fitness room</li>
<li>Bar</li>
<li>Parking (subject to availability, bookable locally) <strong><br /></strong></li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
